- We should call that
the rock star grind.

13:09.289 --> 13:12.582
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

13:12.626 --> 13:16.211
- Adlai working feverishly
to catch up to his competitors.

13:16.254 --> 13:19.047
- I'm not really focused
on what anybody else is doing.

