but when you put them
together with the length,

17:04.357 --> 17:05.773
it doesn't work.

17:05.817 --> 17:08.067
It's very hard
to index properly.

17:08.111 --> 17:10.153
You could actually even
miss your target.

17:10.196 --> 17:12.822
- All right, let's move on
to Jason's blade.

17:12.866 --> 17:16.200
- Just hope they...
like the cleaver idea.

