- Rawr, the giant
cleaver hatchet.

17:19.497 --> 17:20.830
<i> When he wound up</i>
<i> with this theme</i>

17:20.874 --> 17:22.623
<i> of a cleaver for his hatchet,</i>

17:22.667 --> 17:24.667
<i> you know, the idea</i>
