17:31.885 --> 17:34.177
- Okay.
- I think he did a nice job.

17:34.220 --> 17:37.180
Again, different design
but a nice job.

17:37.223 --> 17:39.390
- All right, let's move on
to Rays' blade.

17:39.434 --> 17:41.601
- When I looked over at yours,
I'm like,

17:41.644 --> 17:43.853
"Did he melt that down
