the Forge is...

18:57.762 --> 19:01.472
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

19:01.516 --> 19:03.349
Adlai.

19:03.393 --> 19:05.268
Your hatchet did not
make the cut.

19:05.311 --> 19:07.228
Dave will explain.

19:07.272 --> 19:10.481
- Adlai, I appreciate the design
