19:10.525 --> 19:11.941
<i> but somewhere along the way</i>

19:11.985 --> 19:13.734
you lost control
of that design.

19:13.778 --> 19:15.278
The construction
of your blade

19:15.321 --> 19:18.406
put all that weight
so far forward in the head

19:18.449 --> 19:20.241
that it's just unwieldy,

19:20.285 --> 19:22.243
and that's why
we're letting you go.

19:22.287 --> 19:24.287
- Please surrender your weapon.

19:24.330 --> 19:25.538
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

19:25.582 --> 19:26.998
<i> - I'm disappointed.</i>

19:27.041 --> 19:28.916
I may not be
