20:00.783 --> 20:02.158
from round one,

20:02.202 --> 20:03.951
but I remind you
when the time runs out

20:03.995 --> 20:05.828
and your weapons
have been tested,

20:05.872 --> 20:07.914
one of you will have to
surrender his weapon

20:07.957 --> 20:09.498
