- [laughs]

20:33.441 --> 20:34.982
- I just cut off
about 2 or 3 inches

20:35.026 --> 20:38.027
to cut off on weight and
to increase maneuverability.

20:38.071 --> 20:39.528
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

20:39.572 --> 20:41.572
- All right.

