I can help myself.

21:37.380 --> 21:39.588
[laughs]
I like making big things.

21:39.632 --> 21:41.465
They gave me
a lot of material to use,

21:41.509 --> 21:43.092
and I used it.

21:43.136 --> 21:47.930
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

21:47.974 --> 21:49.765
- The handle's really important.
